reviewText: This movie is hilarious.  Classic comedy, to watch again and again.  Never fails to put me in a good mood.
Great movie I would recommend it to others. Very funny and hilarious. I got to run my amazon.com for a good price.
The movie, My Cousin Vinny, is very funny and entertaining.  We watch it all the time.

Always a great movie to watch!

Great movie funny cast great acting. Great to see Fred Gwynne again. Must have been his last, or close to last, performance. Have seen it many times and never tire of it.
